deliverables.change:
Find the slug display code in renderTrades(). Replace raw slug truncation with:
  const _sp = slugToGameParts(slug);
  const teamDisplay = _sp ? `${_sp.away} @ ${_sp.home}` : (slug ? slug.slice(0, 22) + '…' : '?');
Use teamDisplay in the trade card template instead of the raw slug.

If cmd-winrate element exists but binding is missing, add:
  const wr = s?.r25?.win_rate;
  $('cmd-winrate').textContent = wr != null ? (wr * 100).toFixed(0) + '%' : '—';
